item.title: CVE-2019-11827|2024-09-16T17:39:01.402Z -- synology -- note%20station
item.description: Cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability in SYNO.NoteStation.Shard in Synology Note Station before 2.5.3-0863 allows remote attackers to inject arbitrary web script or HTML via the object_id parameter.
